#: ../../../developers_guide/git/develop.md:10
msgid ""
"Git is an extremely powerful version control tool that supports many "
"different \"workflows\" for individual development and collaboration. Here "
"we document procedures used by the VTK development community. In the "
"interest of simplicity and brevity we do *not* provide an explanation of why "
"we use this approach."
msgstr ""

